{customInstructions}

Rewrite this journal entry to be more coherent, well-structured, and polished while maintaining the author's authentic voice, tone, emotional content, and all important details. Do not change the meaning or add information that wasn't there. Keep the same perspective (first person) and tense. Return ONLY the enhanced entry text, nothing else.

Original entry: "{content}"

writingPrompts.template:
{customInstructions}

Generate 3 thoughtful, creative journal writing prompts. Make them diverse - one introspective, one gratitude-focused, and one future-oriented. Return ONLY a valid JSON array of prompt strings.

Example format: ["What moment today made you pause and appreciate life?", "Describe a challenge you overcame recently.", "What would your ideal day look like one year from now?"]

